Here are several SURFMAP commands to calculate maps with different parametes:

- Basic SURFMAP command to compute map in directory example_1g3n_A_stickiness/:
surfmap -pdb 1g3n_A.pdb -tomap stickiness

- SURFMAP command to compute maps and files in directory example_1g3n_A_stickiness_allfiles/:
surfmap -pdb 1g3n_A.pdb -tomap stickiness --keep

- SURFMAP command to compute maps with residues from file residues_to_map.txt mapped directly on the map in directory example_1g3n_A_stickiness_mapping_residues/:
surfmap -pdb 1g3n_A.pdb -tomap stickiness -res residues_to_map.txt

- SURFMAP command to compute map of bfactor with discrete values (initially developped for binding site mapping) in directory example_1gv3_A_stickiness_binding_sites/:
surfmap -pdb 1gv3_A_binding_sites.pdb -tomap binding_sites
